posts.message: Fun little tool that takes animated snapshots of you when an app error occurs :D It seems to only work for RoR though, no clue if the author intends to support any other frameworks/languages.
posts.caption: blog.oozou.com
posts.description: Inspired by lolcommits which takes a snapshot everytime you git commit code. For fun, we decided to make something similar by taking animated snapshots each time an app error occurs and overlaying the error message on the snapshot. Right now it only supports OS X.
